            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, how blest the love that spared us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For the law had judged us dead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God, to meet the righteous judgment,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Passed it on His Son instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah! Our Redeemer,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ, to God has purchased us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now enjoying His redemption,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We become God’s righteousness."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God is holy in His nature,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Holiness is what He is."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In this way He sanctified us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Makes our nature one with His."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Spreading from our quickened spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He renews each inward part,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Moving into all our being,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Making home in all our heart."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, how blessed is this process!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s the Lord’s life-saving way."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s our constant, real experience;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s our life from day to day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we’re minding just the spirit,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then the mind is life to us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And the Lord in us is gaining"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Transformation marvelous!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Glory is God’s true expression,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All He is, in full, expressed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Final stage of our redemption,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bodily made manifest."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Glory is the consummation"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of this life which sanctifies;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our complete transfiguration"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is the goal which life supplies."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis for this we wait, expecting"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be raptured, glorified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then the earth will see God’s fullness;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ completely testified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We fore’er will just express Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nature will rejoice to see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the sons of God in glory"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Manifested finally."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By His mercy, we’re selected,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ours a glorious destiny."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not by running, nor by willing,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But through God’s own sovereignty."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Once we were wild olive branches,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now the root and fat partake,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Grafted in, rejoice together,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Growing for the kingdom’s sake."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As we’re daily in this process"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And by life are sanctified,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we thank Him for the blessing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of the church life He’s supplied."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Here God is our full enjoyment,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Practical and real to us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sons we are, and heirs together,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the church life, glorious!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
